    "body": "NIXL Mamba disagg has the P-side compute prompt tokens `0..N-1`; the D-side computes token `N` from `h(N-1)` to advance Mamba state correctly.\r\n\r\nThat D-side 1-token row is still marked `is_prefilling` by `num_computed_tokens < num_prompt_tokens`, but there is no reason why it cannot run as a decode.\r\nIn *uniform* 1-token batches, FULL decode CG is selected, while *Mamba still treats the row as prefill*. \r\nMamba prefill is not compatible with FULL CG, causing the observed accuracy drop.\r\n\r\nThis PR makes Mamba classify 1-token prefill rows with prior state as *decodes*. \r\nFirst-token prompts remain prefills.\r\n\r\nTested with the NIXL PD setup from the PR discussion: Main reproduces the GSM8K accuracy drop with CUDA graphs enabled, and this PR recovers expected accuracy.",
    "created_at": "2026-05-12T14:53:31Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-05-19T13:17:11Z",
